```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant FE as 前端 (Next.js)
    participant GW as gateway (Go)
    participant AI as ai (Python)
    participant DS as DashScope 千问
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant RD as Redis
    participant HUB as feed.Hub

    FE->>GW: POST /api/v1/analyze (jwt)
    GW->>GW: Auth → RBAC → Tenant
    GW->>RD: 查热点黑名单缓存
    RD-->>GW: miss
    GW->>AI: POST /v1/analyze

    par 三路并发
        AI->>AI: trace (号段对比)
    and
        AI->>AI: voiceprint (ONNX)
    and
        AI->>DS: classify (千问 LLM)
        DS-->>AI: 5 类标签 + 置信度
    end

    AI->>AI: merge(7:3) → SAFE/WATCH/ALERT/BLOCK
    AI-->>GW: Verdict (json)

    par 异步写
        GW->>DB: INSERT call_logs
    and
        GW->>HUB: Publish(feed.Event)
    end
    GW-->>FE: 200 OK + Verdict

    HUB-->>FE: SSE event: feed (warroom 实时)
```
